==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*ὑποκριτής / hupokritēs / hoop-ok-ree-tace'
*From G5271

===Noun===
'''ὑποκριτής'''

# An actor under an assumed character (stage player), that is, (figuratively) a dissembler (“hypocrite”): - [[hypocrite]].

